$ Azure Database Migration Services

*Simplify on-premises database migration to the cloud*

sa:
  A common scenario to use *Azure Database Migration Services* is to *lift and shift* an on-prem → development/databases/SQL-Server application to
  → Microsoft/Azure/products/SQL-Managed-Instance.

  *Resource Providers* for Azure Database Migration Services include
    • Microsoft.DataMigration
  See also → Windows/PowerShell/command-inventory/noun/az/ResourceProvider/get[`get-azResourceProvider`]
